Text: For all users that live "Down Under" (Oz and NZ), Joan is touring from the 13th to 28th February 2010. See http://joanosborne.com/index.htm?id=17467 for details.

Just another plug for FLAC uploads. It is great to see that miona45 has given us the opportunity to hear Joan uncompressed and in full dynamic voice.
It gives downloaders a chance to burn a CD and play this album in all its purity. And, you can easily convert FLAC to mp3, AAC or ALAC for your iPod if you need. 
I know all uploaders don't have the bandwidth or face download limits. But it's nice to see FLAC. Thanks again.
it took me a little bit to get the hang of flac but it is well worth it. 'How Sweet It Is.'
